item.title: About Civic New Orleans Data Solutions
item.description: Civic New Orleans Data Solutions is a firm providing analytical solutions to organizations in the Greater New Orleans area. Specializing in the non-profit and public sectors, CNODS strives to transform data into action for the benefit of our communities.
